// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5877 — Mass File Rename (silent)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8820c3a3-eda9-55ad-97f7-37503c77b685

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
